    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The most compelling use case for me is with `.iloc` and `.loc`, e.g., `df.iloc[..., 0]`, for users who are writing indexing code that they want to work on data structures of any dimensionality.\n\nI agree this is not so common/useful with pandas itself but it would be nice for cross-compatibility with NumPy and xray.\n"
